routeIdea:
My idea is a route for "The Celtic Way", which is real world.
The  pitch for this route is "A journey through the heart of Celtic culture, exploring the ancient landscapes of Scotland and Ireland, from the Highlands to the Emerald Isle.".
Some ideas for steps are: 
	 - Edinburgh, Scotland to Inverness, Scotland
	 - Inverness, Scotland to Isle of Skye, Scotland
	 - Isle of Skye, Scotland to Belfast, Northern Ireland
	 - Belfast, Northern Ireland to Dublin, Ireland
	 - Dublin, Ireland to Galway, Ireland
